summary: simple  RaceMenu preset of my favorite Dragonborn.
descriptionHtml:
[center][b]About[/b]
Well, since I sold my gaming PC I rarely get to enjoy this anymore, but luckily it runs on this laptop I've had for about a month fairly well. Still can't mod as CK doesn't run on it but I Figured I may as well share my Dragonborn. He has adopted Samuel & Runa from the orphanage, but is presently unmarried.
